BSNL [80] and Airtel [81]  Reliance, Tata, are main providers of terrestrial telephone lines in Chennai. You can make long distance calls from one of the many booths that display NSD/ISD i.e. National Subscriber Dialling (National Long Distance) and International Subscriber Dialling (International Long Distance). Calling cards are also available with these providers which are considerably cheap.


Cell phone rates are one of the cheapest in the world. There are Ten GSM service providers:

